        A Police Clearance Certificate (PCC) in Bahrain is an official document issued by the Bahraini authorities to certify an individual's criminal record or lack thereof within the country.
      </p>
      <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;">
        It serves as proof that the person has not been involved in any criminal activities during their stay in Bahrain. Obtaining a PCC is required for a wide range of purposes including employment, immigration, and education.
      </p>
